            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <div class="text-accent text-4xl mb-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-child"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Kinderen (4-12 jaar)</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Speelse lessen over islamitische waarden, Koran recitatie en basis Arabisch.</p>
                    <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-check text-accent mr-2"></i>
                            Koranles voor kinderen
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-check text-accent mr-2"></i>
                            Arabische taalles
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-check text-accent mr-2"></i>
                            Islamitische etiquette
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <div class="text-accent text-4xl mb-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-graduate"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Jongeren (13-25 jaar)</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Verdiepende studies, sociale activiteiten en persoonlijke ontwikkeling.</p>
                    <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-check text-accent mr-2"></i>
                            Islamitische studies
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-check text-accent mr-2"></i>
                            Mentorschap
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-check text-accent mr-2"></i>
                            Sociale activiteiten
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <div class="text-accent text-4xl mb-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Volwassenen</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Lezingen, workshops en gemeenschapsactiviteiten voor continue educatie.</p>
                    <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-check text-accent mr-2"></i>
                            Tafseer sessies
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-check text-accent mr-2"></i>
                            Hadith studies
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-check text-accent mr-2"></i>
                            Gemeenschapsevents
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/pattern.png')] opacity-5"></div>
            <div class="relative">
                <div class="text-center mb-12">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Aankomende Evenementen</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Blijf op de hoogte van onze activiteiten en evenementen.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div class="bg-base p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                        <div class="text-accent mb-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-calendar text-xl"></i>
                            <span class="ml-2 font-semibold">25 April 2024</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">Ramadan Voorbereidingslezing</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Speciale lezing over de spirituele en praktische voorbereiding op de Ramadan.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="text-accent hover:text-primary transition-colors">Meer informatie →</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-base p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                        <div class="text-accent mb-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-calendar text-xl"></i>
                            <span class="ml-2 font-semibold">1 Mei 2024</span>
                        </div>
